00:50:58.743 --> 00:51:01.530
Because of course,
if d here is 50,000--

00:51:01.530 --> 00:51:03.600
and what I see is
that, in fact, I

00:51:03.600 --> 00:51:07.710
can throw away most of these
measurements and just keep 10--

