00:53:09.120 --> 00:53:12.260
Then you take all
couples of variables.

00:53:12.260 --> 00:53:14.510
Then you get all
triplets of variables.

00:53:14.510 --> 00:53:17.797
And then you find
which one is best.

00:53:17.797 --> 00:53:19.380
From a statistical
point of view there

00:53:19.380 --> 00:53:21.530
